# AgentFrame Consulting Prep — environment template.
# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill only what you use. Everything is OPTIONAL — the system runs without it.
# (Your coding agent provides the LLM. This key powers the non-LLM connector tools.)

# --- Composio: one connection, 100+ tools (Google Docs, Gmail, Calendar, Drive, ...) ---
# Get an `ak_…` key from the Composio dashboard, then connect the apps you want (OAuth).
# Headline use: markdown CV/letter -> editable Google Doc (GOOGLEDOCS_CREATE_DOCUMENT_MARKDOWN).
# Setup details: library/context/connectors.md
COMPOSIO_API_KEY=
